'''vestibule'''

#a [[passage]], [[hall]], or [[room]] between the [[outer]] [[door]] and the [[interior]] of a [[building]]

Also known, infamously as "The Vestibule", a message board by the same name is akin the the entranceway of an elitist club, where all those who are not capable of functioning properly 'inside' are left in "The Vestibule". For reference, see http://boards.ign.com/The_Vestibule/b5296/

A Gateway, to another dimension.

Etymology: Its origin is early 17th century from French, from Latin vestibulum ‘entrance court.’

